00:02:13.733 --> 00:02:14.212
Fine.

00:02:15.464 --> 00:02:16.072
That's it.

00:02:16.648 --> 00:02:17.293
I'll stop.

00:02:18.972 --> 00:02:20.293
If he hadn't saved you,

00:02:20.333 --> 00:02:21.453
I wouldn't have met you.

00:02:21.733 --> 00:02:23.212
I'm grateful. Happy now?

00:02:24.453 --> 00:02:26.092
But you're barely over twenty

00:02:26.532 --> 00:02:28.133
and your beloved has died.

00:02:28.772 --> 00:02:29.733
Heaven has been

00:02:29.932 --> 00:02:30.893
too cruel to you.

00:02:36.492 --> 00:02:37.613
Why the long face?

00:02:39.772 --> 00:02:41.133
I'll cherish you like you

00:02:41.453 --> 00:02:42.053
cherished him.

00:02:45.532 --> 00:02:46.293
