00:03:04.453 --> 00:03:05.613
meant to get married.

00:03:06.092 --> 00:03:07.453
I'll arrange your divorce.

00:03:08.053 --> 00:03:09.733
Since when do you have a say?

00:03:10.212 --> 00:03:11.652
I've always had a say.

00:03:13.733 --> 00:03:14.293
From now on,

00:03:15.453 --> 00:03:16.733
I won't call you stepmother.

00:03:17.293 --> 00:03:18.173
What do you say?

00:03:18.772 --> 00:03:19.613
May I ask your name?

00:03:22.893 --> 00:03:23.532
Feng...

00:03:23.853 --> 00:03:24.812
F-Feng Zuo...

00:03:24.932 --> 00:03:25.652
Wang Feng.

00:03:26.173 --> 00:03:27.613
What a simple and lovely name.

00:03:29.053 --> 00:03:31.053
Wang Feng. Wang Feng.

00:03:31.053 --> 00:03:31.692
Are you done?

00:03:32.212 --> 00:03:33.333
Let's go back.

00:03:33.853 --> 00:03:34.733
I have things to do.

00:03:36.092 --> 00:03:36.932
What's more urgent

00:03:37.092 --> 00:03:38.573
than getting medical treatment?

00:03:39.453 --> 00:03:41.293
I must capture Gu Qianfu and find out

00:03:41.733 --> 00:03:43.293
who commissioned him and whether

00:03:43.733 --> 00:03:44.492
it's related

00:03:45.092 --> 00:03:46.652
to the former Crown Prince.

00:03:48.573 --> 00:03:49.932
We don't have to do it in person.

00:04:01.736 --> 00:04:02.692
Still pooping?

00:04:03.013 --> 00:04:04.424
