00:04:04.812 --> 00:04:05.333
Still?

00:04:05.733 --> 00:04:06.632
None of your business.

00:04:07.613 --> 00:04:08.333
What do you want?

00:04:14.092 --> 00:04:14.772
My bounty.

00:04:15.573 --> 00:04:17.332
You dare ask for payment?

00:04:17.533 --> 00:04:18.012
Why?

00:04:18.173 --> 00:04:19.252
