00:04:58.413 --> 00:04:59.332
Go patch up.

00:04:59.892 --> 00:05:00.892
Will it work?

00:05:13.293 --> 00:05:14.173
My goodness.

00:05:15.132 --> 00:05:17.932
Hexu and Stepmother finally decided

00:05:17.973 --> 00:05:20.533
to defy feudal traditions?

00:05:22.572 --> 00:05:23.173
Fine.

00:05:23.812 --> 00:05:26.012
Today, I will

00:05:26.173 --> 00:05:28.413
safeguard true love.

00:05:33.132 --> 00:05:33.613
You.

00:05:34.093 --> 00:05:34.533
Come here.

00:05:36.812 --> 00:05:37.252
Miss.

00:05:37.293 --> 00:05:37.973
Pass on my word.

00:05:38.053 --> 00:05:39.432
This area's restricted today.

00:05:39.653 --> 00:05:41.213
I'm admiring the moon here.

00:05:41.413 --> 00:05:42.892
Don't disturb me.

00:05:43.533 --> 00:05:44.653
Understood. I'm on it.

00:06:00.372 --> 00:06:02.293
(You were whispering sweet nothings)

00:06:02.372 --> 00:06:04.492
(and canoodling with that evil woman.)

00:06:05.692 --> 00:06:07.132
(She just passed away.)

00:06:07.692 --> 00:06:09.932
(And you're sleeping soundly
like nothing happened.)

00:06:10.653 --> 00:06:12.132
(Heartless brat.)

00:06:13.053 --> 00:06:14.492
(You deserve to die.)

00:06:23.093 --> 00:06:24.093
Perfect timing.

00:06:27.413 --> 00:06:28.132
You're alive?

00:06:39.452 --> 00:06:42.173
You adulterous scums.

00:06:42.760 --> 00:06:44.853
Even that fall didn't kill you?

00:06:45.012 --> 00:06:45.853
This time,

00:06:46.533 --> 00:06:48.653
I must uphold justice.

00:06:55.173 --> 00:06:55.613
Wait.

00:06:57.653 --> 00:06:58.372
What?

00:06:58.613 --> 00:06:59.372
What?

00:06:59.812 --> 00:07:00.252
I was...

00:07:01.093 --> 00:07:01.572
I...

00:07:17.053 --> 00:07:17.653
Stop it.

00:07:18.452 --> 00:07:19.208
Grand Tutor Zhou

00:07:20.053 --> 00:07:20.892
wants me dead. Why?

00:07:21.372 --> 00:07:22.812
If I have offended him,

00:07:22.932 --> 00:07:24.213
I'll apologize to him.

00:07:24.973 --> 00:07:25.533
Mr. Gu.

00:07:26.012 --> 00:07:26.773
Spare me.

00:07:27.932 --> 00:07:29.853
You dare disrespect Grand Tutor Zhou?

00:07:30.173 --> 00:07:31.332
Countless people

00:07:31.533 --> 00:07:32.613
want you dead.

00:07:33.093 --> 00:07:34.892
Grand Tutor wouldn't even
spare you a glance.

00:07:35.452 --> 00:07:35.973
I received

00:07:36.173 --> 00:07:37.053
a mission.

00:07:37.213 --> 00:07:39.173
They said you're utterly wicked

00:07:39.733 --> 00:07:41.293
and wanted you dead.

00:07:43.053 --> 00:07:43.653
How...

00:07:44.053 --> 00:07:45.053
How much did they offer

00:07:45.492 --> 00:07:46.733
to make you hunt me?

00:07:56.653 --> 00:07:57.372
Twenty thousand?

00:07:57.572 --> 00:07:58.452
No way.

00:07:58.733 --> 00:07:59.733
It must be 200,000.

00:08:02.132 --> 00:08:02.773
Two liang.

00:08:11.812 --> 00:08:12.413
What's that?

00:08:13.012 --> 00:08:13.733
Here's ten liang.

00:08:14.293 --> 00:08:15.012
Spare me.

00:08:16.492 --> 00:08:17.932
Take me to your employer.

00:08:18.332 --> 00:08:19.012
And it's yours.

00:08:19.293 --> 00:08:19.812
Deal.

00:08:24.012 --> 00:08:25.132
A real man knows

00:08:25.252 --> 00:08:26.053
when to yield.

00:08:30.012 --> 00:08:31.132
(He's so desperate?)

00:08:39.173 --> 00:08:39.773
What's wrong?

00:08:40.133 --> 00:08:41.773
Who issued Gu Qianfu the murder order?

00:08:42.612 --> 00:08:44.612
I gave Gu Qianfu the order.

00:08:45.092 --> 00:08:46.612
My superior wanted him dead.

00:08:46.852 --> 00:08:48.493
Take me to your superior.

00:08:48.852 --> 00:08:49.972
Let me finish my business.

00:08:50.173 --> 00:08:51.413
And I'll take you to Ms. Li

00:08:51.812 --> 00:08:52.812
from the village.

00:08:56.013 --> 00:08:57.413
I'm Ms. Li. What's wrong?

00:08:57.653 --> 00:08:59.053
You wanted Xue Hexu dead?

00:08:59.373 --> 00:09:00.212
Xue Hexu?

00:09:01.533 --> 00:09:02.293
No idea.

00:09:03.133 --> 00:09:03.852
Good heavens.

00:09:04.133 --> 00:09:06.413
I just do laundry and cooking.

00:09:06.493 --> 00:09:07.572
How could I kill anyone?

00:09:08.452 --> 00:09:11.413
But distributing missions
earns commissions.

00:09:12.653 --> 00:09:13.612
My contact is Mr. Wang

00:09:13.732 --> 00:09:14.932
from the next village.

00:09:15.533 --> 00:09:17.533
I don't know who wants Xue Hexu dead.

00:09:18.773 --> 00:09:20.373
I just received the mission

00:09:20.732 --> 00:09:22.972
from the Broadsword Sect disciple

00:09:23.092 --> 00:09:24.413
Liu Xiaodan.

00:09:26.092 --> 00:09:27.493
We don't have fixed wages

00:09:28.053 --> 00:09:29.493
and earn commissions.

00:09:30.413 --> 00:09:30.972
This month,

00:09:31.332 --> 00:09:33.212
