on the former Crown Prince,

00:09:33.852 --> 00:09:34.773
I'm penniless.

00:09:35.773 --> 00:09:37.212
So I had to take odd jobs.

00:09:39.852 --> 00:09:40.413
In short,

00:09:40.932 --> 00:09:42.133
I've tracked down

00:09:42.332 --> 00:09:43.293
the mission originator.

00:09:45.612 --> 00:09:47.373
Broadsword Sect's Liu Xiaodan.

00:09:47.893 --> 00:09:48.533
Ask him

00:09:48.773 --> 00:09:49.612
whatever you want.

00:09:50.504 --> 00:09:52.424
(Tomb of Liu Xiaodan,
Disciple of Broadsword Sect)

00:09:56.852 --> 00:09:58.893
Gu Qianfu, how dare you tease me?

00:09:59.133 --> 00:10:00.264
How would I know that

00:10:00.264 --> 00:10:00.932
Liu Xiaodan

00:10:00.932 --> 00:10:02.092
