00:10:14.332 --> 00:10:15.852
Need a psychic?

00:10:18.732 --> 00:10:19.773
Business is tough.

00:10:20.013 --> 00:10:21.332
More skills never hurt.

00:10:25.932 --> 00:10:28.092
We still don't know who wants me dead.

00:10:28.452 --> 00:10:29.932
But at least, we paid Gu Qianfu

00:10:29.972 --> 00:10:30.732
to spare my life.

00:10:31.212 --> 00:10:32.133
You can be at ease.

00:10:32.612 --> 00:10:33.092
You fool.

00:10:33.732 --> 00:10:34.493
At this point,

00:10:34.692 --> 00:10:35.932
