00:10:38.212 --> 00:10:39.173
You're terrified

00:10:39.493 --> 00:10:39.972
I'd die?

00:10:43.452 --> 00:10:45.133
Pressing matters await. Come.

00:10:55.612 --> 00:10:56.092
(He...)

00:10:58.373 --> 00:10:59.852
He is the former Crown Prince?

00:11:02.173 --> 00:11:03.773
Days ago, I found his portrait.

00:11:04.493 --> 00:11:05.732
Let's find him and hand him

00:11:06.332 --> 00:11:06.893
