00:11:08.612 --> 00:11:09.092
(No way.)

00:11:09.812 --> 00:11:10.572
(It can't be him.)

00:11:11.253 --> 00:11:12.212
(How could it be him?)

00:11:15.332 --> 00:11:16.253
You know this man?

00:11:17.253 --> 00:11:17.852
No.

00:11:23.893 --> 00:11:24.852
No, I don't.

00:11:25.852 --> 00:11:26.893
(Xue Hexu)

00:11:27.533 --> 00:11:29.092
(is hiding something from me.)

00:11:41.653 --> 00:11:42.653
It's him?

00:11:43.293 --> 00:11:44.932
He's the former Crown Prince!

00:11:50.888 --> 00:11:51.812
(Two years ago)

00:11:51.812 --> 00:11:52.253
Father.

00:11:53.692 --> 00:11:54.253
Look.

00:11:54.452 --> 00:11:55.812
There's something odd.

00:11:56.972 --> 00:11:57.932
Something is sent south

00:11:58.253 --> 00:11:59.812
in the first month every year.

00:12:00.092 --> 00:12:01.092
Sometimes money,

00:12:01.173 --> 00:12:02.133
sometimes textiles,

00:12:02.253 --> 00:12:03.133
sometimes rice.

00:12:03.612 --> 00:12:05.893
At market prices, it's always 500 taels,

00:12:06.332 --> 00:12:07.852
which is enough to sustain

00:12:08.493 --> 00:12:09.732
any commoner for 20 years.

00:12:10.692 --> 00:12:11.293
Hexu.

00:12:12.572 --> 00:12:13.812
I'm providing

00:12:13.932 --> 00:12:17.133
for my former subordinates
who fought for our nation.

00:12:18.293 --> 00:12:19.173
Forget about it.

00:12:20.452 --> 00:12:22.653
We can't spare this expenditure.

00:12:23.932 --> 00:12:24.373
Alright.

00:12:29.493 --> 00:12:31.612
