00:12:32.092 --> 00:12:33.852
on some illegitimate child,

00:12:34.212 --> 00:12:36.373
while neglecting your own children.

00:12:36.893 --> 00:12:38.373
Have you lost your mind?

00:12:38.692 --> 00:12:39.212
Mother.

00:12:39.656 --> 00:12:41.013
Back then, we had no choice

00:12:41.612 --> 00:12:43.293
but to make such a decision.

00:12:43.732 --> 00:12:46.612
After all these years,
many things can't be undone.

00:12:47.253 --> 00:12:49.293
Now we must see this through to the end.

00:12:49.893 --> 00:12:50.332
You...

00:12:56.104 --> 00:12:57.522
(Xue Mansion)

00:13:14.408 --> 00:13:18.496
(Nanwu Town)

00:13:20.533 --> 00:13:21.452
Try this, sir.

00:13:21.932 --> 00:13:22.533
Try it.

00:13:22.692 --> 00:13:24.013
(Nanwu Dock)
Fresh cucumbers, crisp and juicy.

00:13:24.173 --> 00:13:24.852
Try some.

00:13:25.053 --> 00:13:26.253
Try some, sir.

00:13:26.452 --> 00:13:27.612
Crisp and fresh. Try one.

00:13:28.293 --> 00:13:30.332
He wanders around without purpose.

00:13:30.493 --> 00:13:32.533
We can't do anything about him.

00:13:35.133 --> 00:13:35.692
Master,

00:13:35.893 --> 00:13:37.533
please help my useless son.

00:13:38.092 --> 00:13:38.932
Please get up.

00:13:40.456 --> 00:13:45.493
(Xue Youshou, Xue Mansion)

00:13:45.493 --> 00:13:47.173
He's a good child.

00:13:47.653 --> 00:13:49.293
But an evil spirit possessed him

00:13:49.653 --> 00:13:50.692
and corrupted his soul.

00:13:51.133 --> 00:13:52.452
Without immediate intervention,

00:13:53.173 --> 00:13:54.653
disaster will surely follow.

00:13:56.493 --> 00:13:58.293
Your entire clan could be doomed.

00:13:58.893 --> 00:13:59.452
Master,

00:14:00.212 --> 00:14:00.612
so...

00:14:01.053 --> 00:14:03.368
How can we exorcise the evil spirit?

00:14:03.893 --> 00:14:05.773
How to avert this calamity?

00:14:06.092 --> 00:14:07.653
My master cultivated for a millennium

00:14:08.053 --> 00:14:10.612
to build this celestial tower

00:14:10.932 --> 00:14:12.173
with boundless magic.

00:14:13.133 --> 00:14:14.133
Celestial tower?

00:14:14.932 --> 00:14:15.572
Where is it?

00:14:16.293 --> 00:14:17.692
Far as the horizon,

00:14:19.653 --> 00:14:20.812
near as your sight.

00:14:23.413 --> 00:14:24.493
A millennium of cultivation

00:14:24.972 --> 00:14:27.013
for such a small tower?

00:14:30.013 --> 00:14:32.572
Mountains needn't be tall.
With immortals, they become holy.

00:14:33.332 --> 00:14:34.413
Within this tower,

00:14:34.773 --> 00:14:38.092
my master enshrines
the Ultra Supreme Elder Lord.

00:14:39.332 --> 00:14:40.253
Master,

00:14:40.253 --> 00:14:43.013
bury 100 liang of gold under this tree.

00:14:43.732 --> 00:14:45.013
I'll perform rituals daily

00:14:45.293 --> 00:14:46.893
for 49 days.

00:14:47.092 --> 00:14:48.452
Golden pills will form.

00:14:48.572 --> 00:14:49.692
All gold will be returned.

00:14:49.692 --> 00:14:51.493
I'll keep none.

00:14:51.493 --> 00:14:53.533
The pills will be yours.

00:14:54.692 --> 00:14:56.852
One pill per day

00:14:57.092 --> 00:14:57.773
for a month

00:14:58.812 --> 00:15:00.013
should cure your son.

00:15:01.173 --> 00:15:02.253
You charge nothing.

00:15:02.413 --> 00:15:03.493
What a living Buddha.

00:15:03.653 --> 00:15:04.572
I'll bury the gold now.

00:15:04.692 --> 00:15:05.452
Hurry up.

00:15:05.692 --> 00:15:06.152
Hurry.

00:15:18.092 --> 00:15:19.013
My ritual connects

00:15:19.612 --> 00:15:20.773
Heaven and Earth.

00:15:21.253 --> 00:15:22.612
No observers are allowed.

00:15:23.013 --> 00:15:23.493
Master,

00:15:24.013 --> 00:15:25.053
please leave now.

00:15:26.533 --> 00:15:27.572
Thank you, Master.

00:15:45.352 --> 00:15:46.932
This Daoist priest didn't show

00:15:47.092 --> 00:15:48.253
any signs of divine power.

00:15:48.852 --> 00:15:50.092
Exactly.

00:15:50.332 --> 00:15:52.332
Master resorted to this method

00:15:52.533 --> 00:15:53.812
out of desperation.

00:15:55.133 --> 00:15:57.013
He's full of mumbo jumbo.

00:15:57.452 --> 00:15:59.092
Let's keep watch closely.

00:16:01.413 --> 00:16:02.373
By the cosmic decree!

00:16:18.732 --> 00:16:19.812
Thank you, Master.

00:16:35.852 --> 00:16:36.893
Take care, sir.

00:16:37.013 --> 00:16:37.612
Alright.

00:16:40.053 --> 00:16:40.812
Mr. Xue.

00:16:40.972 --> 00:16:42.413
Please come in.

00:16:48.488 --> 00:16:52.084
(Nanwu Beauties)

00:16:53.653 --> 00:16:54.173
Lan.

00:16:55.293 --> 00:16:55.932
Let's begin.

00:16:58.773 --> 00:17:00.053
You can enjoy music anywhere

00:17:00.533 --> 00:17:01.692
with little money.

