00:18:11.372 --> 00:18:12.733
Lan is mine today.

00:18:13.293 --> 00:18:13.773
Get lost.

00:18:30.412 --> 00:18:31.092
Who are you?

00:18:32.533 --> 00:18:33.288
My surname is Xue.

00:18:34.533 --> 00:18:35.293
Lord Dingyuan

00:18:36.053 --> 00:18:36.773
is my father.

00:19:22.132 --> 00:19:22.733
Xue Youshou.

00:19:27.332 --> 00:19:28.172
Pay your rent.

00:19:28.493 --> 00:19:30.412
Two liang. It's been half a year.

00:19:30.892 --> 00:19:32.213
Enough with your tricks.

00:19:32.533 --> 00:19:34.213
Pay today or get out.

00:19:39.652 --> 00:19:40.293
There you go.

00:19:41.572 --> 00:19:42.572
Your impressive demeanor

00:19:42.652 --> 00:19:43.812
really brings honor

00:19:44.132 --> 00:19:45.852
to our humble establishment.

00:19:46.733 --> 00:19:47.213
Come on.

00:19:47.693 --> 00:19:48.213
Hurry.

00:19:48.652 --> 00:19:49.132
Please sit.

00:19:49.412 --> 00:19:49.852
Here.

00:19:51.812 --> 00:19:53.892
Get him some new bedding

00:19:54.053 --> 00:19:54.693
and a tea set.

00:19:54.773 --> 00:19:55.733
Keep the rest.

00:19:56.652 --> 00:19:57.213
Alright.

00:19:57.733 --> 00:20:00.013
I always knew Xue Youshou was blessed.

00:20:00.533 --> 00:20:01.693
I'll work on it now.

00:20:06.053 --> 00:20:07.412
You had 100 liang of gold,

00:20:07.852 --> 00:20:09.572
but can't pay two liang of silver?

00:20:13.013 --> 00:20:13.812
You followed me?

00:20:16.092 --> 00:20:17.973
Let me pay the rent for you.

00:20:19.812 --> 00:20:21.053
So unnecessary.

00:20:22.533 --> 00:20:25.213
Lord Dingyuan Xue Fugui

00:20:26.453 --> 00:20:27.132
is your father?

00:20:29.092 --> 00:20:30.412
Did he tell you that?

00:20:31.652 --> 00:20:32.293
No, he didn't.

00:20:32.933 --> 00:20:33.612
I found out.

00:20:35.293 --> 00:20:35.773
You

00:20:36.572 --> 00:20:37.693
were born to his concubine?

00:20:40.132 --> 00:20:41.053
Concubine?

00:20:44.412 --> 00:20:45.172
Concubine.

00:20:49.693 --> 00:20:51.172
I don't deserve recognition.

00:20:56.013 --> 00:20:57.733
Your mother is the legitimate wife?

00:21:01.572 --> 00:21:02.412
I'm Xue Hexu.

00:21:02.773 --> 00:21:03.453
Second in line.

00:21:04.053 --> 00:21:05.768
I was born with
my twin sister Xue Nuannuan

00:21:06.293 --> 00:21:07.688
on the fifth of the fifth month.

00:21:08.092 --> 00:21:09.933
You seem about my age.

00:21:10.372 --> 00:21:10.984
Your birthday?

00:21:13.013 --> 00:21:14.216
The fifth of the fifth month?

00:21:16.892 --> 00:21:17.332
We were

00:21:18.293 --> 00:21:19.372
born on the same day?

00:21:23.812 --> 00:21:24.812
That is

00:21:27.812 --> 00:21:28.852
my birthday.

00:21:30.372 --> 00:21:31.533
The same day.

00:21:32.612 --> 00:21:34.253
He made them give birth

00:21:34.652 --> 00:21:36.253
on the same day. What an animal.

00:21:36.852 --> 00:21:38.053
Why are you here?

00:21:38.773 --> 00:21:40.973
Not to arrest me, I hope?

00:21:42.933 --> 00:21:43.612
No harm intended.

00:21:44.733 --> 00:21:45.372
Hasn't Father

00:21:47.092 --> 00:21:49.053
ever come looking for you?

00:21:49.453 --> 00:21:50.013
No.

00:21:52.172 --> 00:21:53.412
How cold-hearted.

00:21:55.132 --> 00:21:56.493
He gives you 500 liang yearly,

00:21:56.693 --> 00:21:58.973
yet you live like this?

00:22:00.253 --> 00:22:01.773
I was exiled at seven.

00:22:02.572 --> 00:22:03.372
I was too young

00:22:03.612 --> 00:22:04.652
to manage finances.

00:22:06.132 --> 00:22:07.933
He sent money to a former subordinate.

00:22:08.733 --> 00:22:09.213
But

00:22:10.773 --> 00:22:12.132
he kept it all.

00:22:13.773 --> 00:22:15.372
I couldn't even keep day-old bread,

00:22:15.733 --> 00:22:17.572
let alone have tasty pickles.

00:22:18.493 --> 00:22:19.053
I was eight

00:22:19.892 --> 00:22:21.332
when I started roaming the streets.

00:22:23.652 --> 00:22:24.572
Meanwhile,

00:22:24.812 --> 00:22:27.253
they've been leading a wealthy

00:22:27.973 --> 00:22:28.892
and luxurious life.

00:22:30.253 --> 00:22:31.172
For real?

00:22:34.213 --> 00:22:35.240
I'll get your money back.

00:22:36.933 --> 00:22:37.372
No need.

00:22:39.332 --> 00:22:40.053
I don't want to

00:22:40.332 --> 00:22:41.693
burden your Xue family.

00:22:42.572 --> 00:22:43.693
Perhaps this is

00:22:44.773 --> 00:22:46.132
heaven's punishment for me.

00:22:48.213 --> 00:22:49.092
Why

00:22:49.493 --> 00:22:50.533
are you here exactly?

00:22:51.572 --> 00:22:52.773
To check on you.

00:23:00.812 --> 00:23:01.852
That jade pendant

00:23:02.453 --> 00:23:03.053
looks nice.

00:23:04.053 --> 00:23:05.253
It says "Qinghe" on it.

00:23:05.812 --> 00:23:07.412
There must be another piece

00:23:07.733 --> 00:23:08.493
marked "Zhengming"?

00:23:13.092 --> 00:23:13.933
This is

00:23:14.892 --> 00:23:16.293
the only thing my mother left me.

00:23:18.773 --> 00:23:20.612
It should be treasured.

00:23:21.412 --> 00:23:23.053
Yet I shattered it by mistake.

00:23:24.572 --> 00:23:25.453
But it does have

00:23:25.973 --> 00:23:27.053
the "Zhengming" on it.

00:23:36.053 --> 00:23:36.652
What a pity.

00:23:37.013 --> 00:23:37.933
It's broken.

00:23:39.172 --> 00:23:40.013
But it's pretty.

00:23:44.852 --> 00:23:46.092
You really don't remember me?

